{"tid":1132439,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA警告直徑300米小行星　或被撞範圍跨越半個地球  8年後撞地球","createTime":"2019-04-30T09:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T07:30:27.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d69885c20d1928d59ca8bdb3ae0b861b9b5ecb83","tid":1132439,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190430/photo/bkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190430170123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190430170123&h=505487d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國太空總署（NASA）的研究人員警告，一枚估計直徑達300米的小行星，有可能於2027年4月撞向地球，屆時被撞擊的範圍由美國西部夏威夷橫亙美國本土，跨越大西洋至非洲部分地區。NASA呼籲各國必須及早預備，防範該行星來襲，或一旦地球被撞擊後的應對措施。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名為「行星防禦演習」的會議於周一至周五（4月29日至5月3日）在華盛頓舉行，NASA署長布里登斯廷在會上表示，當局於上月發現一枚代號2019 PDC的小行星，它直徑約有100至300米，於距地球5700萬公里外以秒速14公里飛行。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n署方旗下的噴氣推進實驗室（JPL）與歐洲太空總署（ESA）的監察系統追蹤該行星路徑，最初預計它只有五萬分之一機會撞向地球。惟3周後，他們再經電腦模擬計算，發現該行星撞上地球的機會增加至千分之四。到了周一的最新數據顯示，該行星撞落地球的機會已大增至百分之一；若其運行軌迹不變，預計會在2027年4月29日撞落地球，被撞範圍跨越半個地球。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nESA行星防禦辦公室的科斯尼（Detlef Koschny）表示，2019 PDC撞擊地球的機會雖然看似很微，但各國需及早防備。他表示國際間已有共識，如果小行星體積夠大，會以核彈將它炸碎；但若其直徑少於50米，科學家發現它來襲時可能已沒太多時間，惟有疏散可能被撞擊地區的民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190430/photo/bkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001_02p.jpg?20190430170123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190430%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001_02p.jpg%3F20190430170123&h=084a2efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190430/mobile/bkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190430%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1ROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=eded9d62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190430/mobile/bkn-20190430160850310-0430_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"707cfa166fc938ed6542acfe848ab8f26b90837b","tid":1132439,"uid":192893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:00:52.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"a0b25157f9351d3a9cf2ff955f39d6de0829297c","tid":1132439,"uid":122709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"西方文明盡毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果咁啱計錯數，實際上撞落中國印度+中東<br />\n成個世界清淨哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa0880ba5fb1c98c1d1567954fe8b20cea5ef1e","tid":1132439,"uid":202754,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:05:29.000Z","msg":"make低先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2027年4月29號要早啲搭巴士返工"},{"pid":"89d0a1025b37d58ae404970faa42ff21972b2aae","tid":1132439,"uid":58746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"係就快啦, 由細聽到大, 聽到我三十幾歲都未撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40fb5db676e87e51c4f78552445e981ed4685d3","tid":1132439,"uid":74390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"1%，即係機會大過中六合彩"},{"pid":"ae36c2ff909a87afacd9cccc88130268209979f9","tid":1132439,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b25157f9351d3a9cf2ff955f39d6de0829297c","tid":1132439,"uid":122709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"西方文明盡毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果咁啱計錯數，實際上撞落中國印度+中東<br />\n成個世界清淨哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"都時會唔會多國一齊發支火箭上去控制落點去對方度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27711f2